title: Should You Buy Alphabet Inc Class C (GOOG) Stock Thursday Morning?
text:
Alphabet Inc Class C (GOOG) is higher by Thursday morning, with the stock adding 0.71% in pre-market trading to 151.41. 


GOOG's short-term technical score of 56 indicates that the stock has traded more bullishly over the last month than 56% of stocks on the market. In the Internet Content & Information industry, which ranks 107 out of 146 industries, Alphabet Inc Class C ranks higher than 71% of stocks.
